{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1dfe2649ca","title":"林彪关于加强部队技术训练的谈话","origin":"《林彪元帅文集》（下册），香港凤凰书品， 2016年。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0a15947601","index":0,"year":1960,"month":12,"day":8,"articleId":"1dfe2649ca"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"518e233a92","type":"title","text":"林彪关于加强部队技术训练的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"1dfe2649ca"},{"id":"3dea04676e","type":"paragraph","text":"[林彪听取海军副政治委员杜义德中将汇报后发表的谈话。]","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"1dfe2649ca"},{"id":"671f24e97f","type":"paragraph","text":"要加强对部队的技术训练。海军兵种多，技术复杂，过去发生许多事故，技术水平不高是个很重要的原因，技术水平的提高，是需要一定时间的，尤其像海军这样一个技术复杂的军种，更不是一日之功就可以奏效的。因此，要趁战争未打起前，抓紧时机，拿出大量时间来搞训练。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"1dfe2649ca"}],"page":{"id":"e57a17aaff","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"1dfe2649ca","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}